{"tid":1043371,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"★ g嬸老餅音樂台","createTime":"2019-03-02T08:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T09:59:32.000Z","uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0e6ebe9c70568ef98460526808120d5f67e41783","tid":1043371,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:02:59.000Z","msg":"標題是咪好左d <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N5mT1AIPyKo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN5mT1AIPyKo&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=2a8a3b0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N5mT1AIPyKo</a>"},{"pid":"a5b0984fcc5889cecccf7f7b7f1d0626f7c75d9a","tid":1043371,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:09:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q5IGTVguu40\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq5IGTVguu40&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=1a28894e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q5IGTVguu40</a><br />\n<br />\n點解舊時d鐳射k碟會搵d唱得咁難聽既人唱  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ac4ad49878949af36a23bff8e1cfcf8c2bc0122","tid":1043371,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:14:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/su5IrWCSuAk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fsu5IrWCSuAk&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=bff614f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/su5IrWCSuAk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S-BFPd1QC-Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS-BFPd1QC-Y&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=f9a306a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S-BFPd1QC-Y</a><br />\n<br />\n翻唱或原唱  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"841750ddae23bf8877407b54500618f8b1d7516a","tid":1043371,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:32:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L6YA8ISUzCc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL6YA8ISUzCc&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=9ce8e41c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L6YA8ISUzCc</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VcgoI6-pIfc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVcgoI6-pIfc&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=3811798d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VcgoI6-pIfc</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">叱咤新一代 - 商台二 DJ (1989)</span><br />\n<br />\nCR2在88年321大改革後，口號「商業二台 電台新一代」 89年推出DJ雜錦碟，當中主打的是周美茵林海峰的情歌《只因喜歡你》，後來變成軟硬老人苑的經常笑話，林海峰之後與王菲翻唱成《只因喜歡Faye》，張麗瑾 (鄭丹瑞獨白) 的慘歌《留給最愛的說話》，hit爆K場，多年後張柏芝與陳曉東re-make 《我信韻律全能》是創作人音樂會主題曲，麥天倫《永遠記得》，商台想捧他做迷人聲線小王子，可是後來他不知去向，最hit的當然是軟硬天師，他們的搞笑歌「食嘢一族」開始無厘頭路線，之後再出的唱片成為經典。<br />\n<br />\n愛火廣播站 - 盧業瑂、林姍姍、露比<br />\n留給最愛的說話 - 張麗瑾、鄭丹瑞<br />\n救世者姿勢 - 區新明<br />\n只因喜歡你 - 周美茵、林海峰<br />\n我信韻律全能 - 商業二台DJ<br />\n說句對不起 - 張麗瑾<br />\n永遠記得 - 麥天倫<br />\n你不知道我 - 郭啟華<br />\n世界不會到末日 - 梁穎顏、盧玉鳳、黃志淙<br />\n食嘢一族 - 軟硬天師"},{"pid":"e3b62cafb1b45c5caa0237bc14b798152aa7e7a8","tid":1043371,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>標題是咪好左d <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N5mT1AIPyKo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN5mT1AIPyKo&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=2a8a3b0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N5mT1AIPyKo</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jia0BPYLezM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fjia0BPYLezM&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=aaf640c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jia0BPYLezM</a><br />\n<br />\nmv昨天貼過囉 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7706462ba9ae98dc73018a67782abc23ccc93805","tid":1043371,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T09:39:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gtrLfKZbIRA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgtrLfKZbIRA&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=d844c171\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gtrLfKZbIRA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sWmwI_wxLYM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsWmwI_wxLYM&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=c81ded6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sWmwI_wxLYM</a><br />\n<br />\n杜德偉既歌大家應該聽過，咁杜德智又聽過未 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"676827bbfd84618167fbd1ed76fe34d38fd2fbae","tid":1043371,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:50:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GT0xtVAzCjI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGT0xtVAzCjI&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=a6044f07\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GT0xtVAzCjI</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Qo9LQzR1Lds\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQo9LQzR1Lds&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=a0230db8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Qo9LQzR1Lds</a><br />\n<br />\n尹光（Jackson Wan Kwong），原名呂明光，本地著名歌手，是越南華僑，有「廟街歌王」之稱、高胡大師馮華徒弟。<br />\n<br />\n在越南共和國（南越）出道，為首都西貢堤岸「韶聲音樂社」成員之一。他連自己在內共有八兄弟姊妹（五個已移民美國，兩個仍留在越南發展），小時候家境富裕，當時他的家族在越南開了兩間戲院（豪華戲院、大光戲院）、溜冰場、賣徽章，財力雄厚。而戲院更常播新馬師曾的戲，也曾邀來芳艷芬、何非凡、劉克宣、羅劍龍、林黛等人來到演唱。他七歲開始習粵曲大戲，初期是文武生，後來因越戰爆發，因戰亂或恐怖襲擊頻仍，粵劇台戲容易受到越共恐怖襲擊而式微，因而改為唱曲，其後開始唱粵語流行曲。1969年，尹光以逃兵身份偷渡來港。1975年430事件，他正式移居香港。<br />\n<br />\n2002年，尹光憑一首歌曲《少理阿爸》紅遍全港的士高場所。其後他於2007年演出亞視劇集《靈舍不同》及《十六不搭喜趣來》。"},{"pid":"0b5d4757b0b51bc5edcf67d839bc683c280998e0","tid":1043371,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T11:54:04.000Z","msg":"g嬸你幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44aaf54c692f54f063dad575fc7115b4848465ee","tid":1043371,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:10:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>g嬸你幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n年齡係女人秘密喎 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0013f4386b6140e7403009e61d69c2934407db77","tid":10433